response.overview: Travel to New Orleans with bombshell Anna-Marie Goddard (40th Anniversary Playmate), Hollywood starlet Jenny McCarthy (1994 Playmate of the Year), Laura Cover, Miss October 1998; Karen McDougal, 1998 Playmate of the Year; Brooke Richards, Miss December 1999; Shauna Sand, Miss May 1996; Jaime Bergman, 45th Anniversary Playmate; Stacy Sanches, 1996 Playmate of the Year; and Carrie Stevens, Miss June 1997. It's a curvaceous collection of the world's most bountiful beauties.
response.title: Playboy's Playmates Bustin' Out
